                    <li>3+ years of experience in web development</li>
                    <li>Strong problem-solving skills in Java</li>
                    <li>Open-source contributor</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 text-center">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=80" alt="Coding" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills Section -->
